---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import SimpleFooter from '../components/SimpleFooter.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Wedding - Joel Weinberger" description="Joel and Sarah's wedding, May 30th, 2010">
  <PageHeader title="Wedding" />

  <main class="subpage-shell">
    <section class="prose">
        <p>
          On May 30th, 2010, my wonderful wife, Sarah, and I were married at her
          family's ranch in Westlake Village, CA, just outside of Los Angeles. It
          was a beautiful, sunny, Southern Californian day and an even more
          beautiful occasion. The ceremony was a traditional Jewish wedding,
          preceded by speeches by both the bride and groom to their respective
          wedding parties. The ceremony was followed by an evening of dancing and
          singing and eating under the setting California sun.
        </p>

        <p>
          A day after the wedding, Sarah and I took off on a honeymoon to Italy,
          where we visited Venice, Florence, Tuscany, Umbria, the Amalfi Coast,
          and Rome. We had an amazing time. If you would like to see some photos
          from the honeymoon, please look at our
          <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/metromoxie/sets/72157624953047064" rel="noopener noreferrer">honeymoon photos on Flickr</a>.
        </p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <SimpleFooter />
</BaseLayout>
